&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience in software, algorithms, and system performance engineering, preferably in lidar or related sensor technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong background in signal and image processing, embedded systems, and simulation environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in C++ and Python for algorithm development, performance testing, data analysis, and the ability to read, debug, and modify production code.&lt;/li&gt;
